</p><p>But yes, indirect emissions is fair.  You can't blame electricity companies for the emissions caused by the additional electricity you buy from them, just like we can't blame only fossil fuel companies for the fossil fuels that we consume.

</p><p>All consumers of<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
